{
"cn"
:
"codex 是由 OpenAI 开发的终端 AI 编程代理工具，支持读取本地代码库、运行 shell 命令、生成代码补丁，并以对话方式协助开发任务。\n它可连接 OpenAI API，结合语义理解和上下文感知能力，帮助开发者在终端中快速完成代码生成、重构、调试与测试等操作。\ncodex 支持安全模式、自动批准策略、以及多轮自然语言交互，适用于现代开发流程中的 AI 助手角色。\n项目地址：https://github.com/openai/codex\n"
,
"en"
:
"codex is a terminal-based AI programming assistant developed by OpenAI.\nIt connects to the OpenAI API to understand your local codebase, execute shell commands, generate patches, and assist with development tasks through conversational prompts.\nWith support for secure execution, approval strategies, and contextual code understanding, codex enhances the developer experience by bringing powerful AI assistance directly to your terminal.\nProject: https://github.com/openai/codex\n"
}
